📖 Surah An-Nasr (Victory)

🌟 Taruf:
Ye surah Madni hai.
Qur’an ki aakhri surat me se hai jo Nabi ﷺ ki zindagi ke aakhri hisson me nazil hui.
Isko “Surah at-Tawdi’ (Surah of Farewell)” bhi kaha jata hai,
kyunki isme Nabi ﷺ ke mission ke mukammal hone aur wisaal ke qareeb hone ka ishara hai.

___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

                                                 🌸 بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَٰنِ الرَّحِيمِ🌸
                                                Bismillāhi r-raḥmāni r-raḥīm
                                      Allah ke naam se, jo nihayat Mehrban aur Raheem hai.


🔹 Ayat 1: إِذَا جَاءَ نَصْرُ اللَّهِ وَالْفَتْحُ
“Jab Allah ki madad aur fatah aa jaye.”

➡️ Yahan Allah Ta‘ala Nabi ﷺ ko khush khabri de rahe hain ke Deen Islam ka ghalba hone wala hai.
➡️ Iska sabse bara waqia tha Fatah Makkah (8 Hijri), jab bina khoon bahe Islam ka ghalba hua.
➡️ Nasr = Allah ki madad.
➡️ Fath = Qalbi aur zahiri kamyabi, sab se bara “Fatah Makkah.”

___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🔹 Ayat 2: وَرَأَيْتَ النَّاسَ يَدْخُلُونَ فِي دِينِ اللَّهِ أَفْوَاجًا
“Aur aap dekhenge ke log jamaaton ke jamaaton me Allah ke deen me daakhil ho rahe hain.”

➡️ Fatah Makkah ke baad Arab ke qabeelay dheron dheron Islām qabool karne lage.
➡️ Pehle Islam ahista ahista phail raha tha (individually), lekin Fatah ke baad Islām ek social revolution ki surat me aya.
➡️ Ye Qur’an ka wa‘da tha jo apni poori shaan ke saath pura hua.

___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🔹 Ayat 3: فَسَبِّحْ بِحَمْدِ رَبِّكَ وَاسْتَغْفِرْهُ ۚ إِنَّهُ كَانَ تَوَّابًا
“To apne Rabb ki tasbeeh karo uski hamd ke saath aur us se maghfirat talab karo. Beshak woh Tauba qubool karne wala hai.”

➡️ Jab mission mukammal ho jaye, jab kamyabi mile, us waqt ghamand nahi – Allah ki tasbeeh, shukr aur istighfar karna hai.
➡️ Nabi ﷺ ko hukm diya gaya ke akhir zindagi me zikr aur istighfar ko zyada barhao.
➡️ Ye bhi ek ishara tha ke aap ﷺ ka waqt qareeb hai.

___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

🌷 Dars o ‘Ibrat (Lessons for Us):

👉Victory ka asal source Allah hai – Insaan apni planning kare, lekin kamyabi sirf Allah ki madad se milti hai.
👉Success ka asal shukr hai – Jab Allah niyamat de, to ghamand na ho, balke shukr aur tasbeeh ho.
👉Istighfar ki ahmiyat – Har ibadat aur kam ke baad bhi insaan ko istighfar karna chahiye.

👉Nabi ﷺ khud din me 70–100 martaba istighfar karte the.
👉Mission complete → Reminder of death – Ye surah ye bhi batati hai ke Nabi ﷺ ka mission mukammal ho gaya, ab aap duniya se rukhsat hone wale hain.
👉Islam ki akhri shakal – Surah hume dikhati hai ke Islam fard se qabeelay aur phir ummat ki shakal me aya.

___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

💭 Ek Jumlay ka Khulaasa:

💐Surah An-Nasr hume yeh sikhati hai ke jab Allah ki madad aur kamyabi mile,
   to apni taqat par ghamand na karein, balke Allah ki tasbeeh, shukr aur istighfar karen – yehi haqiqi ibadat hai. 🌸

